{"tid":357474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剛才同個陌生人傾計 佢同我講越南兩蚊美金就有個老婆","createTime":"2017-08-13T01:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T02:11:19.000Z","uid":129509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b57c5e147de406633321c06f8e97605299d73750","tid":357474,"uid":129509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:29:48.000Z","msg":"我諗住學每日都同陌生人傾計個巴打咁，試下接觸陌生人<br />\n個巴打話老人家多數都肯傾，咁我就膽粗粗去同樓下坐撚左係到既阿伯吹下水試下<br />\n一開頭都傾得正正常常，傾傾下佢問得有冇女朋友，我答冇，之後佢就同我講越南兩蚊美金就買到個老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底依個價錢係咩年代既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"f17144d7fac66282a556f4f86e81399a1cc0ee29","tid":357474,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"2010 年代"},{"pid":"a7c14aae8ebf5d9317ca58a09b23a599c3b1e587","tid":357474,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"人地貼錢嫁俾你，嗰兩蚊象牙式收下㗎咋"},{"pid":"8eb1355594634cd8aaa9275c1410f6b1f72f134a","tid":357474,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地貼錢嫁俾你，嗰兩蚊象徵式收下㗎咋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e8fa8988856a63895eed55b48a8af20cb3927862","tid":357474,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/095056_d2fcb31e39732f2d024e3ee78daacebe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F095056_d2fcb31e39732f2d024e3ee78daacebe.jpg&h=87e8c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b21b119c6e16288e48eeb4d363263eeeea981e1","tid":357474,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r